			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I agree with Shanna.  Spend 1 skill point to &quot;learn&quot; the basics of any particular skill.  It will go up rather fast on its own.  And, for starting monks, I would suggest getting a fishing pole and spending some down-time fishing.  It's a simple way to make money which can buy you whatever you may need.  Although, at later levels, I find money to be less and less of a neccesity and more of a luxury.
				</font>
			</td>

