			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Dont bother with a light source in your hand carry a fire beetle eye in your pack, freeing your other hand for more attacks with Dual Wield. Practice Tailoring for money (starting with Wolf and Bear pelts) then join up with groups to tackle Cats for armour for yourself. Save practice points for Feign Death or put lots into Mend. As above 1 point in new skills beyond 1st level. Watchout for Madmen!
				</font>
